data.description: Welcome to your great home in Prosper ISD! This single story 3 bed, 2 bath residence with an office is located in a great school district. The open concept layout creates a seamless flow throughout, providing a spacious living area with high ceilings and abundant natural light. The large kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, storage, walk in pantry, and lots of counter space . The master suite features a large ensuite bathroom with a soaking tub, separate shower, and walk in closet. The two large bedrooms has plenty of room with walk in closets. Step outside to enjoy the backyard with a covered patio. The two car garage features epoxy floors that gives a great look and durability. This home is conveniently situated near the community amenities such as play ground, community fire pits, community gardens, community pool, and tennis court for all types for great fun. This is an exceptional opportunity you won't want to miss!
